	  network configuration if only ifconfig is available

2006-09-04 17:43  lennart

	* man/avahi-autoipd.8.xml.in: describe how to communicate between
	  IPv4LL and non-IPv4LL hosts

2006-09-03 17:26  lennart

	* avahi-autoipd/avahi-autoipd.action: do not remove the interface
	  address if an UNBIND event is recieved. This might accidently
	  remove a manually configured address, hence better don't touch
	  it.

2006-09-03 16:14  lennart

	* avahi-autoipd/avahi-autoipd.action: configure broadcast address
	  explicitly

