	* docs/INSTALL, docs/README: update INSTALL

2006-09-02 16:35  lennart

	* avahi-autoipd/dhclient-enter-hook.in,
	  avahi-autoipd/dhclient-exit-hook.in: remove "set -e" from the
	  hook scripts since this apparently breaks stuff in the main hook
	  script

2006-09-02 16:32  lennart

	* avahi-autoipd/main.c: remove a bogus warning

2006-09-02 14:45  lennart

	* avahi-autoipd, avahi-autoipd/Makefile.am,
	  avahi-autoipd/dhclient-enter-hook.in,
	  avahi-autoipd/dhclient-exit-hook.in: ship dhclient hook scripts
	  for using ipv4ll as fallback solution where DHCP is not
	  available. Only installed on Debian for now, since only Debian
	  provides the necessary hook directories.

