	  0.6.13)

2006-08-31 17:20  lennart

	* avahi-daemon/dbus-protocol.c, avahi-daemon/main.c: Some more
	  s/D-BUS/D-Bus/g

2006-08-31 17:17  lennart

	* avahi-client/client.c, avahi-daemon/dbus-protocol.c,
	  configure.ac: autoconf love:
	  
	  * use autoconf to check whether dbus_connection_close() is
	  available and use it
	  if it is, don't do those checks based on the D-Bus version.
	  
	  * Make use of dbus_bus_get_private() if it is available.
	  
	  * Since D-Bus agreeed on a cononical way to write their name, use
	  that way in
	  configure.ac.
	  
	  * Add configure options to define the UNIX user/group for
	  avahi-autoipd

