	* avahi-daemon/Server.introspect, avahi-daemon/dbus-protocol.c: add
	  new D-Bus API function SetHostName to change the host name of the
	  running avahi daemon

2006-08-22 01:48  lennart

	* avahi-daemon/main.c: fix AVAHI_SERVER_REGISTERING handling

2006-08-22 01:48  lennart

	* avahi-compat-howl/compat.c, avahi-compat-libdns_sd/compat.c,
	  avahi-utils/avahi-publish.c, examples/client-publish-service.c,
	  examples/core-publish-service.c: fix logic of
	  AVAHI_SERVER_REGISTERING state handling. Many clients assumed
	  that
	  this state would follow only on a AVAHI_SERVER_COLLISION state.
	  However, this
	  is not true, hence we need to handle this state transition, too.
	  Mostly the
	  same as we already handle AVAHI_SERVER_COLLISION.

