	* avahi-sharp/Makefile.am: don't define "docdir" which is being
	  defined by autoconf internally

2006-08-21 20:53  lennart

	* avahi-common/alternative-test.c, avahi-common/alternative.c:
	  follow Bonjour's hostname number incrementing algorithm for
	  handling conflicts. On collision the name "foobar" will now
	  become "foobar-2" and not "foobar2". (closes #40)

2006-08-21 20:02  lennart

	* avahi-daemon/main.c: don't remove static services from the avahi
	  daemon on SIGHUP. Add static hosts properly to avahi daemon on
	  SIGHUP. (closes #52)

