	* avahi-core/dns.c: add an extra validity check when parsing mDNS
	  queries and records in packets

2006-04-24 21:52  lennart

	* avahi-common, avahi-common/domain.c: add an utf8 check when
	  unescaping domains - essentially this means that all domain
	  related functions will now consider strings with invalid utf8 as
	  invalid (see #21)

