	  is started before avahi-daemon closing bug #31

2006-04-11 15:52  sebest

	* service-type-database/service-types: add airport entry in
	  service-type db closing #28

2006-04-01 00:48  lennart

	* avahi-core/resolve-service.c: when resolving a service, don't
	  return host name that was assigned to the actual A/AAAA record,
	  but the one specified in the SRV RR. This broke vhost setups with
	  CNAMEs. (This fixes Ubuntu bug 36642)

