2005-08-09 00:32  lennart

	* avahi-common/strlst.c, avahi-common/strlst.h,
	  avahi-daemon/EntryGroup.introspect,
	  avahi-daemon/Server.introspect, avahi-daemon/dbus-protocol.c,
