	  avahi-utils/avahi-publish-service.in,
	  avahi-utils/avahi/__init__.py, docs/HACKING, docs/TODO: * Update
	  HACKING
	  
	  * Change DBUS API: txt record lists are now coded as "aay"
	  instead of "as".
	  Unfortunately this triggers this bug:
	  
	  https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=4023
	  
	  If you want to use avahi-publish-service you need to apply the
	  included patch.
	  
	  * change avahi-bookmarks to listen on 127.0.0.1 only
	  * add ftp and https browsing support to avahi-bookmarks, but
	  disable it due to python-dbus bugs
	  * update avahi module for python to provide functions to convert
	  between tring lists and lists of lists of bytes
	  * add avahi_strlst_add_anonymous()

